channel.title: [PI]Removing Doors?[PI]
channel.description:
OK, I've literally tried/done everything I can..
I CANNOT GET RID OF THIS ****ING CURTAIN..! [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/jgwyy.jpg[/img]
I've gone into PlayerAssistant.java and added the coords of it to the removeObject2 list (the one that is SUPPOSED to delete doors or objects in between spaces)
That didn't work.
I've tried putting the the coords and stuff into ObjectHandler.java and making the object id -1.
That didn't work.
I've tried spawning the open curtain in its place, but the object doesn't appear when I do ::object 1529 ...
So I honestly don't know what else to do, if anyone can help, Rep+ or something idk.
